{"tid":2337794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁子超憂香港變另一個英國 呼籲市民節日期間留家抗疫","createTime":"2020-12-23T14:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T16:28:17.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"53831ec0f2934dd8fddd98570ad5bd958676aa84","tid":2337794,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"梁子超表示，若變種病毒在港落地生根，香港可能變成另一個英國，屆時會由其他國家封鎖。變種病毒傳播力高，而且香港居住環境較外國擠逼，多屋邨及外傭群組，有利病毒傳播。現時最關鍵是市民節日期間留家抗疫，若仍有跨家庭或朋友聚會，病毒有可能進一步擴散，屆時即使再增加檢測也無用。若出現大爆發，可能只能靠接種疫苗作局部圍堵。"},{"pid":"037cd946bed88a82584e62f9fb354c70236d9345","tid":2337794,"uid":168485,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:12:00.000Z","msg":"朋友屋企人唔可以見，同事就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2261ad8adaa721a7b26afb3384508bd5306729eb","tid":2337794,"uid":34869,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:12:39.000Z","msg":"但應該好多香港人想香港變英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd16862fb8e677ff717e419bbcc2d92798f94bb","tid":2337794,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"037cd946bed88a82584e62f9fb354c70236d9345","tid":2337794,"uid":168485,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:12:00.000Z","msg":"朋友屋企人唔可以見，同事就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"我的訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f268ce1710ed2e0bdf901a9bef643aec9ad6d35b","tid":2337794,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:19:22.000Z","msg":"香港本身就係英國, 只係呢23年被支匪侵佔"},{"pid":"1d592f31bbac8dc16a38aca7175f67c8b6d7c410","tid":2337794,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2261ad8adaa721a7b26afb3384508bd5306729eb","tid":2337794,"uid":34869,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:12:39.000Z","msg":"但應該好